  "translations": {
    "en": "Then he said to me: Shall I not tell you more? I said: Yes. He said: When Allah resurrects the believer from his grave, there comes out with him an image leading him. Whenever the believer sees a terror from the terrors of the Day of Judgment, the image says to him: Do not be alarmed and do not grieve, and receive glad tidings of delight and honor from Allah, Mighty and Majestic. And it continues to give him glad tidings of delight and honor from Allah until he stands before Allah, Glory be to Him, and He reckons him an easy reckoning, and orders him to Paradise, and the image before him.",
